                <article class="mcard rv"><div class="mcard-br tl"></div><div class="mcard-br tr"></div><div class="mcard-br bl"></div><div class="mcard-br br2"></div><div class="mcard-n"><span>01 / Email Analysis</span><span>&#8599;</span></div><div class="mcard-ic">&#9993;</div><h3 class="mcard-h">Email Analysis</h3><p class="mcard-p">Forensic email scoring: sender authentication, header anomalies, reply-chain traps, and payload risk signals. Catch spoofing before it reaches the inbox.</p><div class="mcard-tags"><span class="mcard-tag">SPF / DKIM / DMARC</span><span class="mcard-tag">Header Forensics</span><span class="mcard-tag">URL Signals</span></div><div class="mcard-arr">&#8594;</div></article>
